{"tid":552994,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［純學術］屍體處理點樣先可以完美放血？","createTime":"2018-02-07T05:02:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-07T06:21:45.000Z","uid":64564,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3e4cb52becd031a922de79426c846990d0df8282","tid":552994,"uid":64564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T05:02:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實食左佢咪咩事都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>骨呢<br />\n磨埋來食？<br />\n煲到淋哂 搵錘仔揼碎佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc762fb42d0d734a7e386333ff2eefb86f319e02","tid":552994,"uid":82710,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T05:04:42.000Z","msg":"你一餐食得曬咩? <br />\n用鹽防腐啦"},{"pid":"c3f54d96f0e82bab2728e095471abd3691ad748e","tid":552994,"uid":147789,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T05:06:06.000Z","msg":"已報驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eadd150fdba12a4436615dac0193768284f27601","tid":552994,"uid":79137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T05:07:22.000Z","msg":"投入活火山"},{"pid":"1c31d22f1bbd5ed5cb16a9def89f8d104cf32e70","tid":552994,"uid":3688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T05:07:49.000Z","msg":"用鏹水"},{"pid":"a17ec9c2c532335f548fa082289ad181ebae3296","tid":552994,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T05:11:21.000Z","msg":"去屠房做下見習學野<br />\n冇記錯已經死透左就好難放乾淨<br />\n要仲有少少氣時放先得<br />\n<br />\n我當六十公斤，分四五次煮到骨肉分離<br />\n骨就磨粉，肉就分廿幾次當廚餘掉會唔會比較正路"},{"pid":"b15cba031770df3d1ed22bdaed27046d2318918c","tid":552994,"uid":116115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T06:14:48.000Z","msg":"首先你要清楚動脈同靜脈流動方向，動脈同靜脈各開一個口插條管，一邊口放水入去一邊口出水，記得唔可以太快，時間會用得較多，但可以保持到地方乾淨，詳細再問先講"},{"pid":"680d429750f954d1cc53746d0ed629ef9ea05e15","tid":552994,"uid":116115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T06:21:45.000Z","msg":"骨方面可以用醋煲，煲完會好脆，之後再烘乾，可以用焗爐焗到乾，乾到表面變糙就可整碎<br />\n<br />\nps：記得起骨個陣一定一定要由關節位落刀，唔好斬中間，好難斬而且會好嘈"}]}